391
00:31:23,978 --> 00:31:27,878
すぐに指で消した
I quickly erased with my finger

392
00:31:28,878 --> 00:31:30,578
臆病でも
Even if I'm a coward

393
00:31:30,578 --> 00:31:33,178
揺るぎない軌跡
An unwavering trajectory

394
00:31:33,178 --> 00:31:35,678
確かな願いを
With a certain wish

395
00:31:35,678 --> 00:31:38,878
胸に遥か遠く
In my heart, far away

396
00:31:38,878 --> 00:31:41,878
錆び付くように軋んでも
Even if it creaks as if rusting

397
00:31:41,878 --> 00:31:44,978
この真っ暗を灯し進む
I move forward, lighting up this darkness

398
00:31:44,978 --> 00:31:49,178
たった一つ答えを追いかけて
Chasing after the only one answer

399
00:31:50,878 --> 00:31:54,078
脆くても良いこの腕で
Even if they're fragile, with these arms

400
00:31:54,078 --> 00:31:56,978
掴む為に手を伸ばすよ
I'll reach out to grab it

401
00:31:56,978 --> 00:32:00,878
打ち鳴らす鼓動の限り
As long as my heart beats

402
00:32:27,278 --> 00:32:30,878
何度この道で迷って
How many times have I been lost on this road

403
00:32:30,878 --> 00:32:33,978
見失ってどこへ行くの
Lost my way, where am I going?

404
00:32:33,978 --> 00:32:37,978
目指す場所もその意味も
The place I'm aiming for and its meaning

405
00:32:37,978 --> 00:32:41,878
一つしか無いのにな
There is only one, though

406
00:32:41,878 --> 00:32:46,078
曇った視界は
My clouded vision

407
00:32:46,078 --> 00:32:49,978
夜に溶けてもう一度
Dissolves into the night once more

408
00:32:50,778 --> 00:32:53,078
ひらけてゆく
And starts to clear up

409
00:32:53,078 --> 00:32:54,878
視線の先
At the end of my gaze

410
00:32:54,878 --> 00:32:59,278
僕を連れてゆくよきっと
It will surely take me there

411
00:33:03,978 --> 00:33:06,878
深く深く紺になる
It becomes a deep, deep navy

412
00:33:06,878 --> 00:33:09,878
息を吸って今加速を
Take a breath, and now, acceleration

413
00:33:09,878 --> 00:33:14,778
傷付くほどに強くなると
As I become stronger the more I get hurt

414
00:33:15,878 --> 00:33:18,878
確かな色動き出す
A certain color starts to move

415
00:33:18,878 --> 00:33:22,978
纏ってゆけその身体で
Wear it with that body

416
00:33:22,978 --> 00:33:25,878
鮮やかな夜空の果てへ
To the end of the vivid night sky

417
00:33:25,878 --> 00:33:27,978
忘れないように
So I don't forget

418
00:33:27,978 --> 00:33:30,978
深く深く紺になれ
Become a deep, deep navy

419
00:33:30,978 --> 00:33:34,978
今を生きるこの加速度
This acceleration that lives in the now

420
00:33:34,978 --> 00:33:37,878
光だって超えてゆける場所へ
To a place where I can even surpass light

421
00:33:39,978 --> 00:33:42,878
強く強く踏み込んで
Stepping on it strongly, strongly

422
00:33:42,878 --> 00:33:45,878
僕を駆けるただ真っ直ぐに
I dash through, just straight ahead

423
00:33:45,878 --> 00:33:49,878
譲れない想いを抱いて
Embracing feelings I won't give up

424
00:33:49,878 --> 00:33:53,078
止まらないで
Don't stop

425
00:33:53,078 --> 00:33:57,278
走り続ける意味を知るから
Because I know the meaning of continuing to run

426
00:34:09,878 --> 00:34:14,778
わくわくエブリデイ
Waku Waku Everyday

427
00:34:23,178 --> 00:34:26,578
心地よい晴れ空
A pleasant clear sky

428
00:34:27,078 --> 00:34:30,178
今日は何をして遊ぼうか
What should we do for fun today?

429
00:34:30,678 --> 00:34:33,778
いつまでも変わらない
Never changing

430
00:34:33,778 --> 00:34:36,878
雲を追いかけてみようか
Shall we try chasing the clouds?

431
00:34:37,078 --> 00:34:39,978
はしゃぎ回って疲れて
Frolicking around and getting tired

432
00:34:39,978 --> 00:34:42,878
お腹もすいて寝転んで
Getting hungry and lying down

433
00:34:43,778 --> 00:34:47,878
明日はもっといい日になりそう
It looks like tomorrow will be an even better day

434
00:34:47,878 --> 00:34:49,578
一緒だよ
We're together

435
00:34:50,078 --> 00:34:55,278
いつもキラキラ毎日止まらないでしょ
Every day is always sparkling, it won't stop, right?

436
00:34:55,878 --> 00:35:00,778
やりたいこと全部遊び尽くしても
Even if we play through everything we want to do

437
00:35:00,796 --> 00:35:02,861
