See? The excitement doesn't stop, does it?

448
00:36:01,646 --> 00:36:08,296
やりたいこと叶える力があるよ
We have the power to make our wishes come true

449
00:36:08,346 --> 00:36:15,296
そうでしょ？ときめくココロに色づく毎日
Right? Every day colored by a racing heart

450
00:36:15,346 --> 00:36:18,796
君と君と手を取って
Holding hands with you, with you

451
00:36:18,796 --> 00:36:23,796
「今」を重ね続けてこう
Let's keep piling up "nows"

452
00:36:23,846 --> 00:36:28,296
笑顔の帰り道も
Even the way home with a smile

453
00:36:28,346 --> 00:36:31,096
何年経っても
No matter how many years pass

454
00:36:31,146 --> 00:36:35,296
君となら ずっと...
