With you, with you, tomorrow too

464
00:37:31,396 --> 00:37:36,296
ずっと笑えるといいよね
It would be nice if we could keep laughing forever, wouldn't it?

465
00:37:36,346 --> 00:37:40,796
これからも
From now on too

466
00:37:40,846 --> 00:37:45,796
